ust 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: Grandeur is My cloak and pride is My garment. Whoever competes with Me in one of these two, I will cast him into the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4090 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34523,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/27\/evil-within-greed-cowardice\/","url_meta":{"origin":35271,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Vice: Evil within people lies in greed and cowardice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe worst evil within a man is his restless greed and his utmost cowardice.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2511 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15431,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/best-people-initiate-salaam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35271,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Best people initiate greetings of peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the closest to Allah are those who are first to greet with peace.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 5197 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34507,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/21\/best-sadaqah-little-available\/","url_meta":{"origin":35271,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Best charity is given when little is available","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which charity is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne with little property to give. Begin with your dependents.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1677 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u06